author: Zig Ziglar
message: You are the only person on earth who can use your ability.

author: Jean Lacordaire
message: Neither genius, fame, nor love show the greatness of the soul. Only kindness can do that.

author: Carl Jung
message: The least of things with a meaning is worth more in life than the greatest of things without it.
title: Thought of the day

author: Isocrates
message: The noblest worship is to make yourself as good and as just as you can.
title: Thought of the day
